properties.Name: Requisition
properties.Description: A Requisition is an internal document prepared to detail funding and authorization to procure Item(s) via the forthcoming Purchase Order, PO.

Columns.Name: RequisitionId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Requisition.

Columns.Name: RfpId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of the RFP that resulted in generation of the Requisition.

Columns.Name: RfiId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of the RFI that resulted in generation of the Requisition.

Columns.Name: NumberQuotesReceived
Columns.Description: The number of quotes received prior to issuing the associated Requisition.

Columns.Name: RequisitionCreatedDate
Columns.Description: The date that the Requisition was created.

Columns.Name: RequisitionSubmittedDate
Columns.Description: The date that the Requisition was submitted for approval/fulfillment.

Columns.Name: RequisitionApprovedDate
Columns.Description: The date that the Requisition was approved.

Columns.Name: RequisitionSubmittedByName
Columns.Description: The name of the person submitting the Requisition.

Columns.Name: RequisitionAuthorizedByName
Columns.Description: The name of the person authorizing the Requisition.

Columns.Name: RequisitionApprovedByName
Columns.Description: The name of the person approving the Requisition.

Columns.Name: RequestedDeliveryDate
Columns.Description: The requested delivery date of the requisitioned items.

Columns.Name: ConfirmedDeliveryDate
Columns.Description: The confirmed delivery date by the vendor pending the associated PO.

Columns.Name: ActualDeliveryDate
Columns.Description: The actual delivery date of the requisitioned items.

Columns.Name: RequestedPrimaryVendorName
Columns.Description: The primary Vendor requested in the Requisition to fulfill the requisition.

Columns.Name: RequestedSecondaryVendorName
Columns.Description: The secondary Vendor requested in the Requisition to fulfill the requisition.

Columns.Name: RequestedAlternateVendorName
Columns.Description: The alternate Vendor requested to fulfill the Requisition.

Columns.Name: RequisitionServicesProcurementSpecification
Columns.Description: A specification or description of the specifications or details regarding acquisition of services.

Columns.Name: RequisitionTrainingTerms
Columns.Description: A statement describing the Training Terms associated with Requisition.

Columns.Name: RequisitionSupportTerms
Columns.Description: A statement describing the Support Terms associated with Requisition.

Columns.Name: RequisitionInstallationTerms
Columns.Description: A statement describing the Installation Terms associated with Requisition.

Columns.Name: RequisitionAcceptanceTerms
Columns.Description: A statement describing the Acceptance Terms associated with Requisition.

Columns.Name: RequisitionSparePartsTerms
Columns.Description: A statement describing the Spare Parts Terms associated with Requisition.

Columns.Name: RequisitionLicensesAndPermitsTerms
Columns.Description: A statement describing the Licenses and Permit Terms associated with Requisition.

Columns.Name: RequisitionInsuranceTerms
Columns.Description: A statement describing the Insurance Terms associated with Requisition.

Columns.Name: RequisitionTimeAndPenaltiesTerms
Columns.Description: A statement describing the Time and Penalty Terms associated with Requisition.

Columns.Name: RfqId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Request For Quotation.

Columns.Name: RequisitionStatusId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of the Requisition Status.

Columns.Name: ResponsibilityCenterId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Responsibility Center.

Columns.Name: PartyId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Party.

Columns.Name: DocumentId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Document.
